page.title: 08ECOLOGY
page.content: { PLANT LIFE,NATURE,COUNTRYSIDE We compared two environments.20 paces of roadside along the Roman Road, 20 paces of bank along the side of Salty Brook.In both places we found:Bramble, Chickweed,Plantain,Dead nettle,Vetch, Herb Robert,Goose grass,Hogweed, Thistles,Speedwell and Couch grass. Along the roadside we found:Pineapple weed,Stinging nettle,Shepherd's purse, Fat Hen,Pink clover,Cow parsley,Silver weed,Forget-me-not,Milk thistle, Trefoil,Buttercup,Yarrow,Dandelion, Poppy,Cranesbill,Oil-seed-rape,Rye grass,St.Johns Wort,Sweet cicely, Sow thistle,Fescue Tall and Meadow,Cinque foil,Charlock,Goosefoot.Along Salty Brook we found:Nettles,Dog Rose,Woody Nightshade,Burdock,Woundwort,White Campion,Ash,Elder,Alder,watergrass, Hawthorn,Blackthorn,Hedge Maple,Willow Herb,Common reed,Privet,Timothy.
